author: Disney
description:
Hosted by Derek Hough, “The Wonderful World of Disney: Holiday Spectacular” returns for its 10th year, featuring dazzling new musical performances from Walt Disney World Resort in Florida, Disneyland Resort in California, and Aulani, a Disney Resort & Spa in Ko Olina, Hawaiʻi. Narrated by Ginnifer Goodwin (voice of Judy Hopps in “Zootopia 2”), who carries on the tradition of sharing how the Disney Parks sparkle to life for the holidays.

00:00 Derek Hough's Opening Performance
06:34 Gwen Stefani - “Shake the Snow Globe” from Disneyland Resort
11:42 Coco Jones - “Silent Night” from Disney's Animal Kingdom
16:53 Good Charlotte - “Fairytale of New York” at Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge
